Up to you, but you could write:

```dart
for (String channel in <String>['stable', 'dev', 'beta']) {
  testUsingContext('no warning on $channel', () async {
    ...
  }, overrides: <Type, Generator>{
    FlutterVersion: () => MockVersion(channel),
  });
}
```

I suspect the end result is less readable, so entirely fine and maybe better as-is.

